properties.areaDesc: Delaware Bay waters north of East Point NJ to Slaughter Beach DE
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued February 11 at 3:22PM EST until February 12 at 6:00AM EST by NWS Mount Holly NJ
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northwest winds 10 to 15 kt with gusts up to 25 kt.

* WHERE...Delaware Bay waters north of East Point NJ to
Slaughter Beach DE.

* WHEN...From midnight tonight to 6 AM EST Wednesday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM MIDNIGHT TONIGHT TO 6 AM EST WEDNESDAY
